        "subject": "LU-4831 osd-zfs: set block size in __osd_object_create",
        "message": "LU-4831 osd-zfs: set block size in __osd_object_create\n\nIt's more efficient to set block size in\n__osd_object_create(), rather than calling\ndmu_object_set_blocksize() right after\n__osd_object_create() in osd_mkreg().\n\nSigned-off-by: Isaac Huang <he.huang@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I18824bb5198e12b563ec6280f3cd884470c9ad6b\n"
      },
